        },
        "subject": "LU-12916 osd-ldiskfs: detect good extent via extent tree",
        "message": "LU-12916 osd-ldiskfs: detect good extent via extent tree\n\nScanning the page mapping for a good full extent write with\ndelayed allocation may be too expensive.\nTo reduce the CPU usage, we improve it by using Ext4 extent status\ntree (@extent_status) to detect full extent write.\n\nTest-Parameters: forbuildonly\nSigned-off-by: Qian Yingjin <qian@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I605b6c1e3bb1b80fcd331e97170104fc9ef1ecc5\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
